thread.title: Deborah

author: Deborah
title: Deborah
text: Joe Russo from Nelson Alexander, Pascoe Vale handled the sale of our home. He was very professional, and compassionate during some difficult decision making. Joe then assisted with the purchase of my new home. Again he listened to my "wish list" and would contact me with properties that suited and never wasted my time. In my opinion the service provided by Joe was outstanding.
